game.name: Princesses Cake Cooking
game.description:
Princesses Cake Cooking is a wonderfully-designed free online cake recipe game full of fun and entertainment for girls and boys. In this free online cooking game for girls, you will have to decorate cakes for the most beautiful princesses. Take your imagination to a completely new level to create the optimum possible result. You can create the tasty dough of the cake by just following the recipe properly. Let your killing imagination work out to decorate the cake and make it look like a royal piece of dessert. Do not forget to use any of the ingredients since each one has its own role in the composition. 

Your best friend is just waiting for baking a cake. Make sure that you keep the royal theme of the party in your mind while creating a princess cake in this brand new cooking game. You can start it with just checking out the kitchen area and collecting all the needful ingredients. Take a bowl and mix milk, sugar and flour in it. Use another bowl to mix eggs and butter. After completing these tasks, take two mixtures and combine both of them together in order to prepare a nice cake batter. 

Collect three round trays (which are available in different size) and pour the mixture in them. Keep baking them all in the oven placing in the kitchen until they start rising and having a nice golden color. You are suggested to put them on a plate when you see that it is ready to eat. Do not forget to stack them up before moving to the next step. Each layer of the cake is decorated with the help of frosting. Take a chance and add some cute decorations on each layer as well as at the basis of the cake. Also apply a princess broche on the middle part in this best cooking game for girls and boys. Use a crown and a few candles to make it a centrepiece!
